description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 7, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 21, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 8 for East, 8 for South, and 1 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40073-58812-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [21 Votes, Common]
